name: SEXY BLUE BANANAS
description: Sexy Blue Bananas are just like us... They laugh, they sing, they dance, they visit their nana, they go to Sbarro for pizza and pop, they go to school... This is one of the many reasons they shouldn't be eaten, like yellow bananas. That and because they'd go to the trouble of entertaining and feeding you, should you ever decide to visit them at their Carribean home, as well as they're good looking!

name: OPERATION: POTATO MONKEY
description: Potato Monkeys are a rare species known for their big ears and ability to put on quite a show. They are also known for other uncommon characteristics, such as being able to devour three bananas in one sitting and keeping their mothers up until three or four in the morning, tossing their heads back and forth while humming!
